>> >> Patches:
>> >>   3.x: `3ab41641cf6fce3860c73d5cf4645aa12e1e5892`
>> >> (
>> https://github.com/ipython/ipython/commit/3ab41641cf6fce3860c73d5cf4645aa12e1e5892
